      "source": "<a href=\"http://twitter.com/download/iphone\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twitter for iPhone</a>",
      "text": "🚨JUST IN: Dalilah’s Law passed @TransportGOP and is headed to the house floor.\n\nI’m extremely grateful to our strong House Republican leadership, for putting American lives first, and for sweet Dalilah Coleman and her father, Marcus Coleman spearheading this monumental change in trucking safety.  \n\n@RepDavidRouzer’s bill, Dalilah’s Law, is simple: \n🗣️ NO English, NO license\n🚛 States must verify CDLs aren’t issued to illegal immigrants\n👮‍♂️ More penalties for states that failed to comply including federal funding being withheld",
      "text_resolved": "🚨JUST IN: Dalilah’s Law passed @TransportGOP and is headed to the house floor.\n\nI’m extremely grateful to our strong House Republican leadership, for putting American lives first, and for sweet Dalilah Coleman and her father, Marcus Coleman spearheading this monumental change in trucking safety.  \n\n@RepDavidRouzer’s bill, Dalilah’s Law, is simple: \n🗣️ NO English, NO license\n🚛 States must verify CDLs aren’t issued to illegal immigrants\n👮‍♂️ More penalties for states that failed to comply including federal funding being withheld",
